additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Intentional misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents can be harmful or fatal. Keep the unit pointed away from you and others during assembly. Please retain packaging for future reference. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Pressurised dispenser. Extremely flammable. Protect from sunlight and do not expose to temperatures exceeding 50C. Do not pierce or burn, even after use. Keep away from sources of ignition-no smoking. Do not use in asthma or other medical inhalers. Do not use in small confined pet areas.
